Ca - Cavalier                  +     +         Hu 
Ce - Celtic(W/D)      +  +  +                  Hu He 
Cl - Cleric                                    Hu El Dw He Ho Pi Ha Gn 
Dr - Dragoon(T/M/W)   *  *     *  +            Hu He 
Du - Druid                                     Hu He Pi Ha 
