Races are:
Dw = Dwarf        El = Elf         Gi = Giant        Gn = Gnome
Ha = Halfling     He = Half-Elf    Ho = Half-Orc     Hu = Human
Li = Lizardman    Og = Ogre        Pi = Pixie        Tr = Troll
